author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Stop Killing Games, an initiative is a net positive for gamers and the preservation of our favourite titles. PirateSoftware had a lot to say regarding this and I wanted to deconstruct his points and show the public why this initiative matters. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Why PirateSoftware Is Wrong About Stop Killing Games...
